{"tid":1840504,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超冬季窗交白卷 料歐戰難重現「內戰」局面","createTime":"2020-01-25T00:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T08:41:22.000Z","uid":84081,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"acda81bba40d6b5140ff0fd51f47a607085f3de0","tid":1840504,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T00:43:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>利物浦</strong><br />\n<br />\n文尼傷咗、沙拿獨食<br />\n馬體會爛船都有3分釘 <br />\n加上英超仲要12月、1月瘋狂賽程<br />\n442 對 442 利好難輕取<br />\n<br />\n<strong>曼城</strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好玩啦 對住3連冠+拖舟帶既皇馬<br />\n皇馬破唔到密集姐 但曼城既後防大家都知得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n皇馬世一25圖大勇、夏剎特復出<br />\n靜係卡斯米路同華維迪都迫搶到Kdb波皮都掂唔到<br />\n哥狗仲要空運22隻意大利高級G ，自製「波陣困蛟龍」<br />\n估計哥狗歐戰出局後會敗走返巴塞同美斯渡過最後時光了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>李城</strong><br />\n未有歐戰住 有Ndidi要贏維拉入決賽唔難<br />\n<br />\n<strong>車路土</strong><br />\n先講對手拜仁 近況係冇咁穩定 作客都炒熱2-7<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩邊鬥4231既話 古一招同梅拿都高級過Mount<br />\n另一邊廂 林伯成日針對高華碩 唔畀佢同佐做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前場後場唔補強 唔想講了 睇下破唔破到阿對拜既紀錄"},{"pid":"f931a562a8c45059edd1897fe154f6b7f3aa2c33","tid":1840504,"uid":84081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T00:49:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">曼聯</span></strong><br />\n唔講啦 蘇b有未來有歷史<br />\n泊大巴就屌摩佬 蘇b泊就冇野<br />\n行商業路線全球第一 歐戰有冇都冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">熱刺</span></strong><br />\n同RB鬥攻冇Kane仲好 行軍速度仲快<br />\n只要唔好畀足總盃+英超影響到球員冇曬態<br />\n靠兒子一個都可以贏少帥<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">錫菲聯</span></strong><br />\n未有歐戰 全英超防守最強既球隊 <br />\n好好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">阿仙奴</span></strong><br />\n商業足球<br />\n傳控第一季預雞胸 唔駛分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0241de28e68b949adfe49070f86f061c37c7efe4","tid":1840504,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T00:51:34.000Z","msg":"結論<br />\n今年唔會再見英超盛世了"},{"pid":"8a98d28d6f349bc9ed16db1c66a6f6b2e18ab7c2","tid":1840504,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758112b725ec412accd8f94963785e7533fc17a1","tid":1840504,"uid":82938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"原來係你自己分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68acce7795523e52c5664a36dd4dd05a487d07ff","tid":1840504,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"758112b725ec412accd8f94963785e7533fc17a1","tid":1840504,"uid":82938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"原來係你自己分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你點睇？"},{"pid":"13dcd7dcc45f698185ed3e1893d8d1498734b817","tid":1840504,"uid":84081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:00:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">狼隊</span></strong><br />\n呢隊CLS<br />\n勝利11人 冇乜輪換都仲可以反cup修仔<br />\n正常黎講踢咁多咁密已經降咗班<br />\n真心配服 <br />\nRugby佬值得冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯一擔憂都係板凳深度不足 主力一傷就可能出局<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86050910427adaf23c571823966f16fe7cd8df04","tid":1840504,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco